      • OZONE_SCM_HEARTBEAT_LOG_WARN_INTERVAL_COUNT

        public static final String OZONE_SCM_HEARTBEAT_LOG_WARN_INTERVAL_COUNT
        Defines how frequently we will log the missing of heartbeat to a specific SCM. In the default case we will write a warning message for each 10 sequential heart beats that we miss to a specific SCM. This is to avoid overrunning the log with lots of HB missed Log statements.
